msgid "So imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ muduttā kāyassa bhedā sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti. "
msgstr "Because of the weakness of the five faculties, they become fully extinguished when the body breaks up by making extra effort. "

