#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.169:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo diṭṭheva dhamme asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti? "
msgstr "And how does a person become fully extinguished in the present life without making extra effort? "

