msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ … pe … dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe … tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant … enters and remains in the first absorption … second absorption … third absorption … fourth absorption … "

